Locations of the Dorgesh-Kaan chests

Dorgesh-Kaan rich Chests require 78 Thieving and a lockpick to loot. Doing so yields loot and 650 Thieving experience. Chest loot respawns every 300 seconds.

Dorgesh-Kaan average chests also exist in the houses around the city, they have a lower Thieving requirement but do not drop gems.
